PIGAUD.original: ~z~You stay the fuck away from me, asshole. Help me!
PIGAUD.translated: ~z~你丫他妈离我远点，混蛋。来帮我！

PIGAUD.original: ~z~-It's him! It's that fucking guy that kidnapped me.~n~-Lady, I think you're mistaken.
PIGAUD.translated: ~z~－就是他！他就是那个绑架我的狗逼。~n~－女士，我想是你认错人了。

PIGAUD.original: ~z~That motherfucker kidnapped me! Anthony, Sal, Tony, Mark, Benny! Help me!
PIGAUD.translated: ~z~就是那个狗逼绑架了我！Anthony，Sal，Tony，Mark，Benny！来帮我！
